  <bioghist id="aspace_f6f2408942b2bf35fdb38c06d1c9f590">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Doris Tobias (d. 2009) was a food writer based in New York City. She worked as a food and wine columnist and editor for <emph render="italic">Women's Wear Daily</emph> and <emph render="italic">Wine &amp; Spirits Magazine</emph>. Tobias published several cook books and reviewed numerous NYC restaurants during her career. In June 2008, she was interviewed about her 750 square foot East Village apartment for a New York Times article entitled, "LIVING IN A NUTSHELL; Living Large In Little Apple."</p>  </bioghist>
